sort of still somewhat
reasonable outliers within

00:41:28.873 --> 00:41:31.070
the customer ecosystem.

00:41:31.070 --> 00:41:34.180
So you need to find the
customers that are sort of

00:41:34.180 --> 00:41:35.730
at the edge of their
business, or

00:41:35.730 --> 00:41:37.690
at their business model, or
of their industry.

00:41:37.690 --> 00:41:39.770
And find the unique
characteristics about those

00:41:39.770 --> 00:41:43.020
customers, and leverage them
as your early adopters.

00:41:43.020 --> 00:41:45.810
So Paul Graham has a great
article, where he

00:41:45.810 --> 00:41:49.000
talks about living in the
future and building for

00:41:49.000 --> 00:41:51.460
what is missing when you&#39;re
living in the future.

